│ });\n  });\n\n  if (HasMissing)\n    return true;\n\n  // Heuristic: Even if  │
│ we did not find explicit missing instructions, allow\n  // the assertion      │
│ check to succeed. The VPlan and legacy cost models may still\n  //            │
│ legitimately disagree due to differences in how certain predicated or\n  //   │
